  "text": "Since the effectiveness of the friction-free DOB has been verified, in the following experiment, the performance of a motion-copying system using the friction-free DOB when observer pole is increased to 1000 rad/s is investigated. To suppress the noise effect, the friction-free DOB is used in combination with a Kalman filter as shown in Fig. 29 . The Kalman-filter is used for velocity estimation [CITATION_1] , which is an input of the friction-free DOB. The dither frequency is 10 Hz in these experiments.",
